	(text "TRRS jack. full duplex with TX RX crossover in config \nis the default. (SERIAL_USART_FULL_DUPLEX)\nIf you really need an extra pin, \nyou can reconfigure for Serial with TX only."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 146.05 31.75 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
